function info($str) { echo "INFO: $str\n"; }
function warn($str) { echo "WARNING: $str\n"; }
function err($str) { die("FATAL ERROR: $str\n"); }

@set_time_limit(0);

@header('Content-Type: text/plain');

chdir(__DIR__);
$cont = @file_get_contents('changelog.json.php');
if ($cont === false) err('Cannot read changelog.json.php');
$json = @json_decode($cont, true);
if ($json === null) err('Cannot parse changelog.json.php');
$latest_version = false;
foreach ($json as $v) {
	if (isset($v['version']) && (substr($v['version'], -4) != '-dev')) {
		$latest_version = $v['version'];
		break; // the first item is the latest version
	}
}
if ($latest_version != '2.0.1.21') err('This update can only be applied to OIDplus version 2.0.1.21!');

if (version_compare(PHP_VERSION, '7.0.0') < 0) {
	err('You need PHP Version 7.0 to update to this version');
}

// Dir added: userdata/secret
@mkdir('userdata/secret');
if (!is_dir('userdata/secret')) {
	warn('Directory could not be created: userdata/secret');
} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('userdata/secret', 0755)) {
	warn('Could not change directory permissions of userdata/secret');
}

// File added: userdata/secret/info.txt
function writefile_1() {
	@$fp = fopen('userdata/secret/info.txt', 'w');
	@fwrite($fp, base64_decode('DQpBYm91dCB0aGUgZm9sZGVyICJ1c2VyZGF0YS9zZWNyZXQiDQotLS0tLS0tLS0tLS0tLS0tLS0tLS0tLS0tLS0tLS0tLS0tDQoNClRoaXMgZm9sZGVyIGNvbnRhaW5zIHZlcnkgY29uZmlkZW50aWFsIGZpbGVzLA0KZS5nLiBwcml2a2V5X3NlY3JldC5waHAsIHdo'));
	@fwrite($fp, base64_decode('aWNoIGlzIHRoZQ0KZW5jcnlwdGlvbiBrZXkgZm9yIHRoZSBwcml2YXRlIGtleSBzdG9yZWQgaW4gREIuDQo='));
	@fclose($fp);
}
if (is_file('userdata/secret/info.txt') && (sha1_file('userdata/secret/info.txt') != 'ceb60c84d8dc68fccc4c8fb6bc9fcfb80a8523f9')) {
	warn('File was created by someone else. Will overwrite the changes now: userdata/secret/info.txt');
	$tmp = pathinfo('userdata/secret/info.txt');
	$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('userdata/secret/info.txt')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
	warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
	if (!@copy('userdata/secret/info.txt', $backup_name)) {
		warn('Creation of backup failed');
	}
}
writefile_1();
if (!is_file('userdata/secret/info.txt')) {
	warn('File cannot be created (not existing): userdata/secret/info.txt');
} else if (sha1_file('userdata/secret/info.txt') != 'ceb60c84d8dc68fccc4c8fb6bc9fcfb80a8523f9') {
	warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): userdata/secret/info.txt');
} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('userdata/secret/info.txt', 0644)) {
	warn('Could not change file permissions of userdata/secret/info.txt');
}

if (!is_file('.gitignore')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: .gitignore');
	writefile_4();
	if (!is_file('.gitignore')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): .gitignore');
	} else if (sha1_file('.gitignore') != '198330ed5fb2e8ac221806531dfa5a064ebab104') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): .gitignore');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('.gitignore', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of .gitignore');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('.gitignore') !== '198330ed5fb2e8ac221806531dfa5a064ebab104') {
		if (@sha1_file('.gitignore') !== 'd232975f846a58081965a53e28e0831f169ec04b') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: .gitignore');
			$tmp = pathinfo('.gitignore');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('.gitignore')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('.gitignore', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_4();
		if (@sha1_file('.gitignore') !== '198330ed5fb2e8ac221806531dfa5a064ebab104') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): .gitignore');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('ajax.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: ajax.php');
	writefile_5();
	if (!is_file('ajax.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): ajax.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('ajax.php') != '1ec1ec7aa550c26544587e0b4e2fffd8856c06ff') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): ajax.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('ajax.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of ajax.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('ajax.php') !== '1ec1ec7aa550c26544587e0b4e2fffd8856c06ff') {
		if (@sha1_file('ajax.php') !== '714446c245507a62b6da58a32e8b6222f1df39a2') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: ajax.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('ajax.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('ajax.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('ajax.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_5();
		if (@sha1_file('ajax.php') !== '1ec1ec7aa550c26544587e0b4e2fffd8856c06ff') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): ajax.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_access')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: dev/generate_wellknown_other_access');
	writefile_10();
	if (!is_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_access')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): dev/generate_wellknown_other_access');
	} else if (sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_access') != '174819885ff5294b7366d7ee5e11cae92dd78508') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): dev/generate_wellknown_other_access');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('dev/generate_wellknown_other_access', 0755)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of dev/generate_wellknown_other_access');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_access') !== '174819885ff5294b7366d7ee5e11cae92dd78508') {
		if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_access') !== 'fa8b7cb09c93abd61901fe21702b16e78c5b1b69') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: dev/generate_wellknown_other_access');
			$tmp = pathinfo('dev/generate_wellknown_other_access');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('dev/generate_wellknown_other_access')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('dev/generate_wellknown_other_access', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_10();
		if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_access') !== '174819885ff5294b7366d7ee5e11cae92dd78508') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): dev/generate_wellknown_other_access');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_firebird')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: dev/generate_wellknown_other_firebird');
	writefile_11();
	if (!is_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_firebird')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): dev/generate_wellknown_other_firebird');
	} else if (sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_firebird') != 'b1eec36abbfb99e17b412602ad8b81237a88f907') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): dev/generate_wellknown_other_firebird');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('dev/generate_wellknown_other_firebird', 0755)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of dev/generate_wellknown_other_firebird');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_firebird') !== 'b1eec36abbfb99e17b412602ad8b81237a88f907') {
		if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_firebird') !== '0a5108eeb445b15aafea2501c2b5915d70b3e1ef') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: dev/generate_wellknown_other_firebird');
			$tmp = pathinfo('dev/generate_wellknown_other_firebird');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('dev/generate_wellknown_other_firebird')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('dev/generate_wellknown_other_firebird', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_11();
		if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_firebird') !== 'b1eec36abbfb99e17b412602ad8b81237a88f907') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): dev/generate_wellknown_other_firebird');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql');
	writefile_12();
	if (!is_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql');
	} else if (sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql') != '1bc35252ad964b358b297442516130a44b4d10f7') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql', 0755)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql') !== '1bc35252ad964b358b297442516130a44b4d10f7') {
		if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql') !== '33f517c021a86a2b957767949f2675eb2d2cab86') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql');
			$tmp = pathinfo('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_12();
		if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql') !== '1bc35252ad964b358b297442516130a44b4d10f7') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql');
	writefile_13();
	if (!is_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql');
	} else if (sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql') != 'b9cbd953c8018096c7490699cb19a790c7f2189c') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql', 0755)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql') !== 'b9cbd953c8018096c7490699cb19a790c7f2189c') {
		if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql') !== '349b154075200bdd857a5a65ab1396713696840b') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql');
			$tmp = pathinfo('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_13();
		if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql') !== 'b9cbd953c8018096c7490699cb19a790c7f2189c') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_oracle')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: dev/generate_wellknown_other_oracle');
	writefile_14();
	if (!is_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_oracle')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): dev/generate_wellknown_other_oracle');
	} else if (sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_oracle') != '2fcd00d69d7252e627f378dee4d8fe4aee19624b') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): dev/generate_wellknown_other_oracle');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('dev/generate_wellknown_other_oracle', 0755)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of dev/generate_wellknown_other_oracle');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_oracle') !== '2fcd00d69d7252e627f378dee4d8fe4aee19624b') {
		if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_oracle') !== '1e16017701573e5b457dfd2ef2c8eaa100752108') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: dev/generate_wellknown_other_oracle');
			$tmp = pathinfo('dev/generate_wellknown_other_oracle');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('dev/generate_wellknown_other_oracle')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('dev/generate_wellknown_other_oracle', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_14();
		if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_oracle') !== '2fcd00d69d7252e627f378dee4d8fe4aee19624b') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): dev/generate_wellknown_other_oracle');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql');
	writefile_15();
	if (!is_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql');
	} else if (sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql') != '6dd34e47e4e754ac59662ab7823cba6c12a7c654') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql', 0755)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql') !== '6dd34e47e4e754ac59662ab7823cba6c12a7c654') {
		if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql') !== '0452ce55c1ee704ebbb09e33accd9cc86d5e64c5') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql');
			$tmp = pathinfo('dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_15();
		if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql') !== '6dd34e47e4e754ac59662ab7823cba6c12a7c654') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_sqlite')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: dev/generate_wellknown_other_sqlite');
	writefile_16();
	if (!is_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_sqlite')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): dev/generate_wellknown_other_sqlite');
	} else if (sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_sqlite') != 'cc6401f0debc13702175c05b0a814c1218fdd16d') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): dev/generate_wellknown_other_sqlite');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('dev/generate_wellknown_other_sqlite', 0755)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of dev/generate_wellknown_other_sqlite');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_sqlite') !== 'cc6401f0debc13702175c05b0a814c1218fdd16d') {
		if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_sqlite') !== 'e470f5f5ff1c81773b420843324abae4ca5cca66') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: dev/generate_wellknown_other_sqlite');
			$tmp = pathinfo('dev/generate_wellknown_other_sqlite');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('dev/generate_wellknown_other_sqlite')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('dev/generate_wellknown_other_sqlite', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_16();
		if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_sqlite') !== 'cc6401f0debc13702175c05b0a814c1218fdd16d') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): dev/generate_wellknown_other_sqlite');
		}
	}
}

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: doc/developer_notes/compatibility_notes.md');
	writefile_17();
	if (!is_file('doc/developer_notes/compatibility_notes.md')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): doc/developer_notes/compatibility_notes.md');
	} else if (sha1_file('doc/developer_notes/compatibility_notes.md') != '2187d9443a8218d1a3c899cfa7ecd83a61c7a819') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): doc/developer_notes/compatibility_notes.md');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('doc/developer_notes/compatibility_notes.md', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of doc/developer_notes/compatibility_notes.md');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('doc/developer_notes/compatibility_notes.md') !== '2187d9443a8218d1a3c899cfa7ecd83a61c7a819') {
		if (@sha1_file('doc/developer_notes/compatibility_notes.md') !== 'ec86ca03fee50bc47fc4ae30abdd120909762a83') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: doc/developer_notes/compatibility_notes.md');
			$tmp = pathinfo('doc/developer_notes/compatibility_notes.md');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('doc/developer_notes/compatibility_notes.md')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('doc/developer_notes/compatibility_notes.md', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_17();
		if (@sha1_file('doc/developer_notes/compatibility_notes.md') !== '2187d9443a8218d1a3c899cfa7ecd83a61c7a819') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): doc/developer_notes/compatibility_notes.md');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
	writefile_19();
	if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php') != '267a63dd81f91b6f427f94068de47eede1396ed3') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php') !== '267a63dd81f91b6f427f94068de47eede1396ed3') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php') !== '4346f4fe640ae0f0b747ee9b60b7c6a23150f2b7') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_19();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php') !== '267a63dd81f91b6f427f94068de47eede1396ed3') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
		}
	}
}

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/classes/OIDplusConfigInitializationException.class.php');
	writefile_22();
	if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplusConfigInitializationException.class.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/classes/OIDplusConfigInitializationException.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusConfigInitializationException.class.php') != '4b6305d4ebc359c14c6c8b39ca3fc548e2d666ea') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusConfigInitializationException.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/classes/OIDplusConfigInitializationException.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/classes/OIDplusConfigInitializationException.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusConfigInitializationException.class.php') !== '4b6305d4ebc359c14c6c8b39ca3fc548e2d666ea') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusConfigInitializationException.class.php') !== '6c5a93991b4bbf5eb9cf2c11290463627d855ee0') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/classes/OIDplusConfigInitializationException.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/classes/OIDplusConfigInitializationException.class.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/classes/OIDplusConfigInitializationException.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/classes/OIDplusConfigInitializationException.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_22();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusConfigInitializationException.class.php') !== '4b6305d4ebc359c14c6c8b39ca3fc548e2d666ea') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusConfigInitializationException.class.php');
		}
	}

if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplusGui.class.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/classes/OIDplusGui.class.php');
	writefile_23();
	if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplusGui.class.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/classes/OIDplusGui.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusGui.class.php') != 'e743e302e4b80ced0606980ceb971435e344cb4b') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusGui.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/classes/OIDplusGui.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/classes/OIDplusGui.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusGui.class.php') !== 'e743e302e4b80ced0606980ceb971435e344cb4b') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusGui.class.php') !== '467803aeeafe7bce8ab02779acbef74395c19986') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/classes/OIDplusGui.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/classes/OIDplusGui.class.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/classes/OIDplusGui.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/classes/OIDplusGui.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_23();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusGui.class.php') !== 'e743e302e4b80ced0606980ceb971435e344cb4b') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusGui.class.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('oidplus.min.css.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: oidplus.min.css.php');
	writefile_24();
	if (!is_file('oidplus.min.css.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): oidplus.min.css.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('oidplus.min.css.php') != 'a48aaafbe33ed594a8207173bbf110952621dd9c') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): oidplus.min.css.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('oidplus.min.css.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of oidplus.min.css.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('oidplus.min.css.php') !== 'a48aaafbe33ed594a8207173bbf110952621dd9c') {
		if (@sha1_file('oidplus.min.css.php') !== '64ae64f5c8cc87501b7d640c9251ec51e0ead6e5') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: oidplus.min.css.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('oidplus.min.css.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('oidplus.min.css.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('oidplus.min.css.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_24();
		if (@sha1_file('oidplus.min.css.php') !== 'a48aaafbe33ed594a8207173bbf110952621dd9c') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): oidplus.min.css.php');
		}
	}
}

	writefile_31();
	if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/901_vnag_version_check/vnag.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/901_vnag_version_check/vnag.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/901_vnag_version_check/vnag.php') != 'f2254d63aba6ede570b9c0a230cff41c6bb1942d') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/901_vnag_version_check/vnag.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/901_vnag_version_check/vnag.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/901_vnag_version_check/vnag.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/901_vnag_version_check/vnag.php') !== 'f2254d63aba6ede570b9c0a230cff41c6bb1942d') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/901_vnag_version_check/vnag.php') !== '23ae5b899e4622c0a58c50a2a303f63e42451623') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/901_vnag_version_check/vnag.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/901_vnag_version_check/vnag.php');

			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/901_vnag_version_check/vnag.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_31();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/901_vnag_version_check/vnag.php') !== 'f2254d63aba6ede570b9c0a230cff41c6bb1942d') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/901_vnag_version_check/vnag.php');

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/viathinksoft/database/sqlite3/OIDplusDatabasePluginSQLite3.class.php');
	writefile_37();
	if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/database/sqlite3/OIDplusDatabasePluginSQLite3.class.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/database/sqlite3/OIDplusDatabasePluginSQLite3.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/database/sqlite3/OIDplusDatabasePluginSQLite3.class.php') != '84d3f827334b2e00dbeeda40806d28c7d976b04c') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/database/sqlite3/OIDplusDatabasePluginSQLite3.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/database/sqlite3/OIDplusDatabasePluginSQLite3.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/database/sqlite3/OIDplusDatabasePluginSQLite3.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/database/sqlite3/OIDplusDatabasePluginSQLite3.class.php') !== '84d3f827334b2e00dbeeda40806d28c7d976b04c') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/database/sqlite3/OIDplusDatabasePluginSQLite3.class.php') !== 'c225a4679499f5a72a9da078e0b77402c3213b92') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/database/sqlite3/OIDplusDatabasePluginSQLite3.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/database/sqlite3/OIDplusDatabasePluginSQLite3.class.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/viathinksoft/database/sqlite3/OIDplusDatabasePluginSQLite3.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/database/sqlite3/OIDplusDatabasePluginSQLite3.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_37();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/database/sqlite3/OIDplusDatabasePluginSQLite3.class.php') !== '84d3f827334b2e00dbeeda40806d28c7d976b04c') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/database/sqlite3/OIDplusDatabasePluginSQLite3.class.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
	writefile_38();
	if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml') != '6102fd5ff54ce299aeac7ff89991491d425cd646') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml') !== '6102fd5ff54ce299aeac7ff89991491d425cd646') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml') !== '388b7c92c3948601ab06990e0340a3df493524b0') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_38();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml') !== '6102fd5ff54ce299aeac7ff89991491d425cd646') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
		}
	}
}

			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/100_whois/whois/json/security.inc.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/100_whois/whois/json/security.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_46();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/100_whois/whois/json/security.inc.php') !== '1accb82296fd86f094c94ff44e3a1e573fe82a6f') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/100_whois/whois/json/security.inc.php');
		}
	}
}

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/500_resources/show_icon.php');
	writefile_48();
	if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/500_resources/show_icon.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/500_resources/show_icon.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/500_resources/show_icon.php') != '044620ca2add57b3fa7c8af2365de333262a8a33') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/500_resources/show_icon.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/500_resources/show_icon.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/500_resources/show_icon.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/500_resources/show_icon.php') !== '044620ca2add57b3fa7c8af2365de333262a8a33') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/500_resources/show_icon.php') !== '3a345e0e61c46b2c21a0da6b6845bf695e75d525') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/500_resources/show_icon.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/500_resources/show_icon.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/500_resources/show_icon.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/500_resources/show_icon.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_48();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/500_resources/show_icon.php') !== '044620ca2add57b3fa7c8af2365de333262a8a33') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/500_resources/show_icon.php');
		}
	}
}

	writefile_49();
	if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/access/sql/wellknown_country.sql')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/access/sql/wellknown_country.sql');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/access/sql/wellknown_country.sql') != '88fa738da497fd7d6d4fdc0893a9a4787b573194') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/access/sql/wellknown_country.sql');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/access/sql/wellknown_country.sql', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/access/sql/wellknown_country.sql');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/access/sql/wellknown_country.sql') !== '88fa738da497fd7d6d4fdc0893a9a4787b573194') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/access/sql/wellknown_country.sql') !== '7916b2d5a485dfbe7dfe636fc9a50718b8cd79a5') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/access/sql/wellknown_country.sql');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/access/sql/wellknown_country.sql');

			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/access/sql/wellknown_country.sql', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_49();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/access/sql/wellknown_country.sql') !== '88fa738da497fd7d6d4fdc0893a9a4787b573194') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/access/sql/wellknown_country.sql');

}

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/access/sql/wellknown_other.sql');
	writefile_50();
	if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/access/sql/wellknown_other.sql')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/access/sql/wellknown_other.sql');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/access/sql/wellknown_other.sql') != '1edc333ae20b3ed60cef04b2f9f5d5cbc144ec13') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/access/sql/wellknown_other.sql');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/access/sql/wellknown_other.sql', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/access/sql/wellknown_other.sql');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/access/sql/wellknown_other.sql') !== '1edc333ae20b3ed60cef04b2f9f5d5cbc144ec13') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/access/sql/wellknown_other.sql') !== 'c895d41fe83974098292c80c2386e66a4a644a38') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/access/sql/wellknown_other.sql');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/access/sql/wellknown_other.sql');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/access/sql/wellknown_other.sql')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/access/sql/wellknown_other.sql', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_50();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/access/sql/wellknown_other.sql') !== '1edc333ae20b3ed60cef04b2f9f5d5cbc144ec13') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/access/sql/wellknown_other.sql');
		}

	writefile_51();

		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/firebird/sql/wellknown_country.sql');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/firebird/sql/wellknown_country.sql') != '5fdcb657a6ac224635d5ae06cd58855e4ea1da2c') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/firebird/sql/wellknown_country.sql');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/firebird/sql/wellknown_country.sql', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/firebird/sql/wellknown_country.sql');
	}

	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/firebird/sql/wellknown_country.sql') !== '5fdcb657a6ac224635d5ae06cd58855e4ea1da2c') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/firebird/sql/wellknown_country.sql') !== '220d6fe4b66609f0aefb6e43ae0d6877c9aee991') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/firebird/sql/wellknown_country.sql');

		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/firebird/sql/wellknown_country.sql') !== '5fdcb657a6ac224635d5ae06cd58855e4ea1da2c') {

if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/firebird/sql/wellknown_other.sql')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/firebird/sql/wellknown_other.sql');
	writefile_52();
	if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/firebird/sql/wellknown_other.sql')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/firebird/sql/wellknown_other.sql');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/firebird/sql/wellknown_other.sql') != '81c720222255902db6e42742ca6f87406bd51c3d') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/firebird/sql/wellknown_other.sql');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/firebird/sql/wellknown_other.sql', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/firebird/sql/wellknown_other.sql');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/firebird/sql/wellknown_other.sql') !== '81c720222255902db6e42742ca6f87406bd51c3d') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/firebird/sql/wellknown_other.sql') !== '03cf74b4b70e93ce5f7234fac8c996c4afd7abbf') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/firebird/sql/wellknown_other.sql');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/firebird/sql/wellknown_other.sql');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/firebird/sql/wellknown_other.sql')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/firebird/sql/wellknown_other.sql', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_52();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/firebird/sql/wellknown_other.sql') !== '81c720222255902db6e42742ca6f87406bd51c3d') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/firebird/sql/wellknown_other.sql');
		}
	}
}

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mssql/sql/wellknown_country.sql');
	writefile_53();
	if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mssql/sql/wellknown_country.sql')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mssql/sql/wellknown_country.sql');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mssql/sql/wellknown_country.sql') != 'b0b06512b98a0a8846855385131f60ea1e6935d3') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mssql/sql/wellknown_country.sql');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mssql/sql/wellknown_country.sql', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mssql/sql/wellknown_country.sql');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mssql/sql/wellknown_country.sql') !== 'b0b06512b98a0a8846855385131f60ea1e6935d3') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mssql/sql/wellknown_country.sql') !== '77e2322610cadbc00f1058e52bae9b546b429f46') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mssql/sql/wellknown_country.sql');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mssql/sql/wellknown_country.sql');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mssql/sql/wellknown_country.sql')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mssql/sql/wellknown_country.sql', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_53();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mssql/sql/wellknown_country.sql') !== 'b0b06512b98a0a8846855385131f60ea1e6935d3') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mssql/sql/wellknown_country.sql');
		}
	}
}

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mssql/sql/wellknown_other.sql');
	writefile_54();
	if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mssql/sql/wellknown_other.sql')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mssql/sql/wellknown_other.sql');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mssql/sql/wellknown_other.sql') != '43a60c887478a858a76661722e6a75e1427194c4') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mssql/sql/wellknown_other.sql');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mssql/sql/wellknown_other.sql', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mssql/sql/wellknown_other.sql');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mssql/sql/wellknown_other.sql') !== '43a60c887478a858a76661722e6a75e1427194c4') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mssql/sql/wellknown_other.sql') !== '8f501af5e864be93a436716b9a54a19bcbd970e6') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mssql/sql/wellknown_other.sql');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mssql/sql/wellknown_other.sql');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mssql/sql/wellknown_other.sql')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mssql/sql/wellknown_other.sql', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_54();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mssql/sql/wellknown_other.sql') !== '43a60c887478a858a76661722e6a75e1427194c4') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mssql/sql/wellknown_other.sql');
		}

}

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mysql/sql/wellknown_country.sql');
	writefile_55();
	if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mysql/sql/wellknown_country.sql')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mysql/sql/wellknown_country.sql');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mysql/sql/wellknown_country.sql') != '91cf699cc5c3851ac44eddba3d2099b35a46b938') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mysql/sql/wellknown_country.sql');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mysql/sql/wellknown_country.sql', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mysql/sql/wellknown_country.sql');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mysql/sql/wellknown_country.sql') !== '91cf699cc5c3851ac44eddba3d2099b35a46b938') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mysql/sql/wellknown_country.sql') !== 'f623f9514769bd5446351a86cef494fb7d3c761f') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mysql/sql/wellknown_country.sql');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mysql/sql/wellknown_country.sql');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mysql/sql/wellknown_country.sql')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');

			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mysql/sql/wellknown_country.sql', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_55();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mysql/sql/wellknown_country.sql') !== '91cf699cc5c3851ac44eddba3d2099b35a46b938') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mysql/sql/wellknown_country.sql');

if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mysql/sql/wellknown_other.sql')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mysql/sql/wellknown_other.sql');
	writefile_56();
	if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mysql/sql/wellknown_other.sql')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mysql/sql/wellknown_other.sql');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mysql/sql/wellknown_other.sql') != 'a95b80440f1c3ba15df7166b59c517436a4f00ac') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mysql/sql/wellknown_other.sql');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mysql/sql/wellknown_other.sql', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mysql/sql/wellknown_other.sql');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mysql/sql/wellknown_other.sql') !== 'a95b80440f1c3ba15df7166b59c517436a4f00ac') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mysql/sql/wellknown_other.sql') !== '00ff5b1e9ca4228bde9efeaa7d127273616d3503') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mysql/sql/wellknown_other.sql');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mysql/sql/wellknown_other.sql');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mysql/sql/wellknown_other.sql')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mysql/sql/wellknown_other.sql', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_56();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mysql/sql/wellknown_other.sql') !== 'a95b80440f1c3ba15df7166b59c517436a4f00ac') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/mysql/sql/wellknown_other.sql');
		}
	}
}

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/oracle/sql/wellknown_other.sql');
	writefile_58();
	if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/oracle/sql/wellknown_other.sql')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/oracle/sql/wellknown_other.sql');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/oracle/sql/wellknown_other.sql') != 'bdca7e3cc719c8d84ad6d8958f087eeba5e3b061') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/oracle/sql/wellknown_other.sql');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/oracle/sql/wellknown_other.sql', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/oracle/sql/wellknown_other.sql');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/oracle/sql/wellknown_other.sql') !== 'bdca7e3cc719c8d84ad6d8958f087eeba5e3b061') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/oracle/sql/wellknown_other.sql') !== '9d816c08837b05263606134b2a0cc711614475b0') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/oracle/sql/wellknown_other.sql');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/oracle/sql/wellknown_other.sql');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/oracle/sql/wellknown_other.sql')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/oracle/sql/wellknown_other.sql', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_58();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/oracle/sql/wellknown_other.sql') !== 'bdca7e3cc719c8d84ad6d8958f087eeba5e3b061') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/oracle/sql/wellknown_other.sql');
		}
	}
}

	writefile_59();

		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/pgsql/sql/wellknown_country.sql');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/pgsql/sql/wellknown_country.sql') != '6128be65709f1d2cb2d3e48473a5cce229c43f5f') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/pgsql/sql/wellknown_country.sql');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/pgsql/sql/wellknown_country.sql', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/pgsql/sql/wellknown_country.sql');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/pgsql/sql/wellknown_country.sql') !== '6128be65709f1d2cb2d3e48473a5cce229c43f5f') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/pgsql/sql/wellknown_country.sql') !== 'f8fe1111cd97ecc8b1b83858c45bdea000f7d5c0') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/pgsql/sql/wellknown_country.sql');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/pgsql/sql/wellknown_country.sql');

			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/pgsql/sql/wellknown_country.sql', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_59();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/pgsql/sql/wellknown_country.sql') !== '6128be65709f1d2cb2d3e48473a5cce229c43f5f') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/pgsql/sql/wellknown_country.sql');

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/pgsql/sql/wellknown_other.sql');
	writefile_60();
	if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/pgsql/sql/wellknown_other.sql')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/pgsql/sql/wellknown_other.sql');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/pgsql/sql/wellknown_other.sql') != 'ca5e9e55db1d9c60bdc2d5fb8a440076d0198a86') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/pgsql/sql/wellknown_other.sql');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/pgsql/sql/wellknown_other.sql', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/pgsql/sql/wellknown_other.sql');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/pgsql/sql/wellknown_other.sql') !== 'ca5e9e55db1d9c60bdc2d5fb8a440076d0198a86') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/pgsql/sql/wellknown_other.sql') !== 'edf006b7bb34b0366de0f6aa0cfd1354c3e728d3') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/pgsql/sql/wellknown_other.sql');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/pgsql/sql/wellknown_other.sql');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/pgsql/sql/wellknown_other.sql')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/pgsql/sql/wellknown_other.sql', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_60();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/pgsql/sql/wellknown_other.sql') !== 'ca5e9e55db1d9c60bdc2d5fb8a440076d0198a86') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/pgsql/sql/wellknown_other.sql');
		}
	}
}

// Files different: plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/sqlite/sql/wellknown_country.sql

	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/sqlite/sql/wellknown_country.sql') !== 'bedd99676c515b53f8b9dc588200ef20478f869b') {

			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/sqlite/sql/wellknown_country.sql');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/sqlite/sql/wellknown_country.sql');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/sqlite/sql/wellknown_country.sql')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');

			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/sqlite/sql/wellknown_country.sql', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_61();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/sqlite/sql/wellknown_country.sql') !== 'bedd99676c515b53f8b9dc588200ef20478f869b') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/sqlite/sql/wellknown_country.sql');

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/sqlite/sql/wellknown_other.sql');
	writefile_62();
	if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/sqlite/sql/wellknown_other.sql')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/sqlite/sql/wellknown_other.sql');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/sqlite/sql/wellknown_other.sql') != '2f622592d892ba1d580a37e4ff4300d3213b58b9') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/sqlite/sql/wellknown_other.sql');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/sqlite/sql/wellknown_other.sql', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/sqlite/sql/wellknown_other.sql');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/sqlite/sql/wellknown_other.sql') !== '2f622592d892ba1d580a37e4ff4300d3213b58b9') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/sqlite/sql/wellknown_other.sql') !== 'ac9979bc8b6f621a027fdc27383037461e07c57f') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/sqlite/sql/wellknown_other.sql');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/sqlite/sql/wellknown_other.sql');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/sqlite/sql/wellknown_other.sql')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/sqlite/sql/wellknown_other.sql', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_62();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/sqlite/sql/wellknown_other.sql') !== '2f622592d892ba1d580a37e4ff4300d3213b58b9') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/sqlSlang/sqlite/sql/wellknown_other.sql');
		}
	}
}

	if (!is_file('polyfill.min.js.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): polyfill.min.js.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('polyfill.min.js.php') != '1ce8902c025dc4dc23aa6f7f5469bd6fbc14b7d1') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): polyfill.min.js.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('polyfill.min.js.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of polyfill.min.js.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('polyfill.min.js.php') !== '1ce8902c025dc4dc23aa6f7f5469bd6fbc14b7d1') {
		if (@sha1_file('polyfill.min.js.php') !== 'e3b63edbbbb1680521d3f925d938418597f1b956') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: polyfill.min.js.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('polyfill.min.js.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('polyfill.min.js.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('polyfill.min.js.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_63();
		if (@sha1_file('polyfill.min.js.php') !== '1ce8902c025dc4dc23aa6f7f5469bd6fbc14b7d1') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): polyfill.min.js.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('setup/index.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: setup/index.php');
	writefile_64();
	if (!is_file('setup/index.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): setup/index.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('setup/index.php') != 'eaadef87cf65733a96c3dd177df5c32a7c61de95') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): setup/index.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('setup/index.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of setup/index.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('setup/index.php') !== 'eaadef87cf65733a96c3dd177df5c32a7c61de95') {
		if (@sha1_file('setup/index.php') !== 'e49b63a01fcc22ed6a9bb6da79a70b2524be6fec') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: setup/index.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('setup/index.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('setup/index.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('setup/index.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_64();
		if (@sha1_file('setup/index.php') !== 'eaadef87cf65733a96c3dd177df5c32a7c61de95') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): setup/index.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('vendor/composer/installed.json')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: vendor/composer/installed.json');
	writefile_68();
	if (!is_file('vendor/composer/installed.json')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): vendor/composer/installed.json');
	} else if (sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.json') != 'e09df9e40da411af10a7b104fddc7a63a7484877') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): vendor/composer/installed.json');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('vendor/composer/installed.json', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of vendor/composer/installed.json');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.json') !== 'e09df9e40da411af10a7b104fddc7a63a7484877') {
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.json') !== '082a47be4f75637017a64943f871e205dcc84fd5') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: vendor/composer/installed.json');
			$tmp = pathinfo('vendor/composer/installed.json');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('vendor/composer/installed.json')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('vendor/composer/installed.json', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_68();
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.json') !== 'e09df9e40da411af10a7b104fddc7a63a7484877') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): vendor/composer/installed.json');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('vendor/composer/installed.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: vendor/composer/installed.php');
	writefile_69();
	if (!is_file('vendor/composer/installed.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): vendor/composer/installed.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.php') != 'ebb09cdd299f6ea087f2511c2938c36e7b2b983f') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): vendor/composer/installed.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('vendor/composer/installed.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of vendor/composer/installed.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.php') !== 'ebb09cdd299f6ea087f2511c2938c36e7b2b983f') {
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.php') !== 'fabcf6b000df7a3a51923edfa9141cc316b88dbd') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: vendor/composer/installed.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('vendor/composer/installed.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('vendor/composer/installed.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('vendor/composer/installed.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_69();
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.php') !== 'ebb09cdd299f6ea087f2511c2938c36e7b2b983f') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): vendor/composer/installed.php');
		}
	}
}

			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('vendor/danielmarschall/php_utils/oid_utils.inc.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('vendor/danielmarschall/php_utils/oid_utils.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_70();
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/danielmarschall/php_utils/oid_utils.inc.php') !== '6b401d16d0732413fcd5478f98a58b4a6ce6232f') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): vendor/danielmarschall/php_utils/oid_utils.inc.php');
		}
	}
}

		warn('Could not change file permissions of vendor/paragonie/constant_time_encoding/src/RFC4648.php');
	}

	if (@sha1_file('vendor/paragonie/constant_time_encoding/src/RFC4648.php') !== 'e71fa87f84214a42415ff1df0a3415a38b8cc2a9') {

			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: vendor/paragonie/constant_time_encoding/src/RFC4648.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('vendor/paragonie/constant_time_encoding/src/RFC4648.php');

			}

			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): vendor/paragonie/constant_time_encoding/src/RFC4648.php');

	if (!is_file('vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Crypt/Common/Formats/Keys/OpenSSH.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Crypt/Common/Formats/Keys/OpenSSH.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Crypt/Common/Formats/Keys/OpenSSH.php') != 'bbcecc586fa2017b9f42e7b232b4891173862be2') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Crypt/Common/Formats/Keys/OpenSSH.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Crypt/Common/Formats/Keys/OpenSSH.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Crypt/Common/Formats/Keys/OpenSSH.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Crypt/Common/Formats/Keys/OpenSSH.php') !== 'bbcecc586fa2017b9f42e7b232b4891173862be2') {
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Crypt/Common/Formats/Keys/OpenSSH.php') !== '1f799532dfc41aa2683196aa63b1133a8432ad4a') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Crypt/Common/Formats/Keys/OpenSSH.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Crypt/Common/Formats/Keys/OpenSSH.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Crypt/Common/Formats/Keys/OpenSSH.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Crypt/Common/Formats/Keys/OpenSSH.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_80();
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Crypt/Common/Formats/Keys/OpenSSH.php') !== 'bbcecc586fa2017b9f42e7b232b4891173862be2') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Crypt/Common/Formats/Keys/OpenSSH.php');
		}
	}
}




echo 'DONE'; // This exact string will be compared in Update v3

@unlink(__FILE__);
if (is_file(__FILE__)) warn('Could not delete '.basename(__FILE__).'! Please delete it manually');
